1. To run the project call project1("path/to/image_file_name").
2. Select the operation that has to be performed. 
3. A new window will open once all the computation is completed(might take a few minutes).
The image on the left is the grayscale image of the input image. The image on the right is the output image.

Notes:
The various functions have been tested with Octave(ver >= 3.4). They may or maynot be compatible with Matlab.